#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:5
msgid ""
"This is the first release candidate of v0.17.0 for vLLM Ascend. Please "
"follow the [official doc](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest)"
" to get started."
msgstr ""
"这是 vLLM Ascend v0.17.0 的第一个候选发布版本。请按照[官方文档](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest)开始使用。"

