#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:154
msgid ""
"**NPU Graph EX (npugraph_ex) Enabled by Default**: The npugraph_ex "
"feature is now enabled by default, providing better graph optimization "
"with integrated inductor pass and MatmulAllReduceAddRMSNorm fusion. "
"[#6354](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6354) "
"[#6664](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6664) "
"[#6006](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6006)"
msgstr "**NPU Graph EX (npugraph_ex) 默认启用**：npugraph_ex 功能现已默认启用，通过集成的 inductor pass 和 MatmulAllReduceAddRMSNorm 融合提供更好的图优化。 [#6354](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6354) [#6664](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6664) [#6006](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6006)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:155
