"[#4188](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/4188) "
"[#4458](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/4458) "
"[#5848](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5848)"

