"[#3848](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/3848) "
"[#3778](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/3778) "
"[#5390](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5390)"

