#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:480
msgid ""
"Add async exponential while model executing. [#4501](https://github.com"
"/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/4501)"
msgstr ""
"在模型执行时添加异步指数 [#4501](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/4501)"

