"`response_format` 参数暂不支持，我们将很快提供支持。 "
"[#4175](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/4175)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:650
msgid ""
"cpu bind feature doesn't work for multi instance case(Such as multi DP on"
