#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:667
msgid ""
"MTP > 1 is supported now. [#2708](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/2708)"
msgstr ""
"现已支持 MTP > 1。 [#2708](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/2708)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:668
msgid ""
"[Experimental] Graph mode `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` is supported now! And `FULL`"
