"ascend/pull/2309)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:770
msgid ""
"Qwen3 MoE/Qwen2.5 support torchair graph now. [#2403](https://github.com"
"/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/2403)"
