"Qwen3 MoE/Qwen2.5 现已支持 torchair 图模式。[#2403](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/2403)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:771
msgid ""
"Support Sliding Window Attention with AscendSceduler, thus fixing Gemma3 "
