"/vllm-ascend/pull/1582)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:898
msgid ""
"Kimi-K2 with w8a8 quantization, Qwen3-Coder and GLM-4.5 is supported in "
"vLLM Ascend, please following this [tutorial](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/v0.10.0rc1/docs/source/tutorials/multi_node_kimi.md) to have "
