msgstr ""
"添加了 with_prefill CPU allreduce 以处理 D 节点重计算 [#2129](https://github.com"
"/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/2129)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:1039
msgid ""
"Added D2H & initRoutingQuantV2 to improve prefill perf in "
