#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:1113
msgid ""
"Atlas 300I series is experimental supported in this release (Functional "
"test passed with Qwen2.5-7b-"
"instruct/Qwen2.5-0.5b/Qwen3-0.6B/Qwen3-4B/Qwen3-8B). "
