"Upgrade vLLM to 0.9.1 [#1165](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/1165)"
msgstr ""
"将 vLLM 升级至 0.9.1 [#1165](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/1165)"

