#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:1259
msgid ""
"This is the 1st release candidate of v0.8.5 for vllm-ascend. Please "
"follow the [official doc](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/tree/v0.8.5rc1) to start the journey. Now you can enable V1 egnine"
