"/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/v0.8.5rc1/docs/source/user_guide/suppoted_features.md)."
msgstr ""
"这是 vllm-ascend v0.8.5 的第一个候选发布版本。请按照[官方文档](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/tree/v0.8.5rc1)开始使用。现在，您可以通过设置环境变量 `VLLM_USE_V1=1` 来启用 V1 引擎。vLLM Ascend 的功能支持状态请参见 [supported_features](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/v0.8.5rc1/docs/source/user_guide/suppoted_features.md)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:1263
msgid ""
"Upgrade CANN version to 8.1.RC1 to support chunked prefill and automatic "
