"Upgrade vLLM to 0.8.5.post1 [#715](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/715)"
msgstr "将 vLLM 升级到 0.8.5.post1 [#715](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/715)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:1270
msgid ""
"Fix early return in CustomDeepseekV2MoE.forward during profile_run "
